{"tid":1330510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府取消與中學生聚會","createTime":"2019-07-18T14:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T15:07:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e06c4294d851623a6e075011e1328e69c324e59d","tid":1330510,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:58:17.000Z","msg":"有網上討論區流傳，有民政事務局曾聯絡中學生，周五在政府總部與官員會面。民政事務局晚上回覆傳媒查詢時說，政府將不會在明天舉辦青年人與官員的聚會。 <br />\n<br />\n局方表示，政府會透過不同途徑接觸不同背景的人士，包括年輕人，以廣泛聆聽不同意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469133-20190718.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469133-20190718.htm&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE%2FFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=cf18faf1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469133-20190718.htm&h=6dbb6e2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469133-20190718.htm</a>"},{"pid":"62c4b7764551b4269aed95fc1c18a7d10b7b70ea","tid":1330510,"uid":266231,"like":0,"dislike":52,"score":-52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48e484e4f8d089fbac799aa5d5ee4b79be2545a1","tid":1330510,"uid":73826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"【\b721文宣】星期日前一齊做鍵盤戰士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327641</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXAdLRx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXAdLRx.jpg&h=988ba3dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aw6P3Dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faw6P3Dd.jpg&h=545a2bea&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MxBsQid.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxBsQid.jpg&h=0a25f5ce&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DEt65Rz